  {
    "annotations": {
      "destructiveHint": false,
      "idempotentHint": true,
      "openWorldHint": false,
      "readOnlyHint": true,
    },
    "description": "Use this when:
- You want to inspect how notes connect across a topic or project
- You are evaluating whether relationships are too sparse or too dense

Do not use this when:
- You only need one note; use \`get\`
- You only need ranked topic matches; use \`recall\`

Returns: memory nodes and relationship edges for the requested slice.

Typical next step:
- Use \`get\`, \`relate\`, \`unrelate\`, or \`consolidate\` based on what the graph reveals.",
    "inputSchema": {
      "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
      "properties": {
        "cwd": {
          "description": "Absolute path of the project working directory. Required for project-scoped routing, vault selection, and search boosting.",
          "type": "string",
        },
        "limit": {
          "default": 25,
          "maximum": 50,
          "minimum": 1,
          "type": "integer",
        },
        "scope": {
          "default": "all",
          "enum": [
            "project",
            "global",
            "all",
          ],
          "type": "string",
        },
        "storedIn": {
          "default": "any",
          "description": "Filter by vault storage label like list tool.",
          "enum": [
            "project-vault",
            "main-vault",
            "any",
            "attached",
          ],
          "type": "string",
        },
      },
      "type": "object",
    },
    "name": "memory_graph",
    "outputSchema": {
      "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "properties": {
        "action": {
          "const": "graph_shown",
          "type": "string",
        },
        "limit": {
          "type": "number",
        },
        "nodes": {
          "items": {
            "additionalProperties": false,
            "properties": {
              "edges": {
                "items": {
                  "additionalProperties": false,
                  "properties": {
                    "toId": {
                      "type": "string",
                    },
                    "type": {
                      "enum": [
                        "related-to",
                        "explains",
                        "example-of",
                        "supersedes",
                        "derives-from",
                        "follows",
                      ],
                      "type": "string",
                    },
                  },
                  "required": [
                    "toId",
                    "type",
                  ],
                  "type": "object",
                },
                "type": "array",
              },
              "id": {
                "type": "string",
              },
              "title": {
                "type": "string",
              },
            },
            "required": [
              "id",
              "title",
              "edges",
            ],
            "type": "object",
          },
          "type": "array",
        },
        "project": {
          "additionalProperties": false,
          "properties": {
            "id": {
              "type": "string",
            },
            "name": {
              "type": "string",
            },
          },
          "required": [
            "id",
            "name",
          ],
          "type": "object",
        },
        "truncated": {
          "type": "boolean",
        },
      },
      "required": [
        "action",
        "nodes",
        "limit",
        "truncated",
      ],
      "type": "object",
    },
    "title": "Memory Graph",
  },
  {
    "annotations": {
      "destructiveHint": false,
      "idempotentHint": true,
      "openWorldHint": false,
      "readOnlyHint": false,
    },
    "description": "Use after \`where_is_memory\` or \`get\` confirms a memory is stored in the wrong place.

Use this when:
- A note is stored in the wrong place
- Project-specific knowledge should move between shared project storage and main storage
- A note should live in a specific sub-vault such as \`.mnemonic-lib\`

Do not use this when:
- You only need to edit the note content; use \`update\`
- You want to delete the note; use \`forget\`

Returns: moved id, from/to vault labels, project association, persistence status.

Writable attachments: can move notes in writable attached vaults.

[mutating: moves note between vaults, may adjust project association, git commits, may push]

Typical next step:
- Use \`where_is_memory\` or \`get\` to verify the final state.
- Use \`relate\` if the moved memory connects to existing notes in the new vault.",
    "inputSchema": {
      "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
      "properties": {
        "allowProtectedBranch": {
          "description": "One-time override for protected branch checks. When true, move_memory can commit on a protected branch without changing project policy.",
          "type": "boolean",
        },
        "cwd": {
          "description": "Absolute path of the project working directory. Required for project-scoped routing, vault selection, and search boosting.",
          "type": "string",
        },
        "id": {
          "description": "Exact memory id. Use an id returned by \`recall\`, \`list\`, \`recent_memories\`, or \`where_is\`.",
          "pattern": "^[a-zA-Z0-9_-]+$",
          "type": "string",
        },
        "target": {
          "description": "Destination: 'main-vault' for private/global storage, 'project-vault' for shared project storage",
          "enum": [
            "main-vault",
            "project-vault",
          ],
          "type": "string",
        },
        "vaultFolder": {
          "description": "Optional target project vault folder name, such as \`.mnemonic-lib\`. Use this only when moving into a specific sub-vault instead of the primary project vault.",
          "type": "string",
        },
      },
      "required": [
        "id",
        "target",
      ],
      "type": "object",
    },
    "name": "move_memory",
    "outputSchema": {
      "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "properties": {
        "action": {
          "const": "moved",
          "type": "string",
        },
        "fromVault": {
          "pattern": "^main-vault$|^project-vault$|^sub-vault:\\.mnemonic-.+$|^attached:[a-z0-9][-a-z0-9]*\\/\\.mnemonic(-.+)?$",
          "type": "string",
        },
        "id": {
          "type": "string",
        },
        "metadataRewritten": {
          "type": "boolean",
        },
        "persistence": {
          "additionalProperties": false,
          "properties": {
            "durability": {
              "enum": [
                "local-only",
                "committed",
                "pushed",
              ],
              "type": "string",
            },
            "embedding": {
              "additionalProperties": false,
              "properties": {
                "model": {
                  "type": "string",
                },
                "reason": {
                  "type": "string",
                },
                "status": {
                  "enum": [
                    "written",
                    "skipped",
                  ],
                  "type": "string",
                },
              },
              "required": [
                "status",
                "model",
              ],
              "type": "object",
            },
            "embeddingPath": {
              "type": "string",
            },
            "git": {
              "additionalProperties": false,
              "properties": {
                "commit": {
                  "enum": [
                    "committed",
                    "skipped",
                    "failed",
                  ],
                  "type": "string",
                },
                "commitBody": {
                  "type": "string",
                },
                "commitError": {
                  "type": "string",
                },
                "commitMessage": {
                  "type": "string",
                },
                "commitOperation": {
                  "enum": [
                    "add",
                    "commit",
                  ],
                  "type": "string",
                },
                "commitReason": {
                  "type": "string",
                },
                "push": {
                  "enum": [
                    "pushed",
                    "skipped",
                    "failed",
                  ],
                  "type": "string",
                },
                "pushError": {
                  "type": "string",
                },
                "pushReason": {
                  "type": "string",
                },
              },
              "required": [
                "commit",
                "push",
              ],
              "type": "object",
            },
            "notePath": {
              "type": "string",
            },
            "retry": {
              "additionalProperties": false,
              "properties": {
                "attemptedCommit": {
                  "additionalProperties": false,
                  "properties": {
                    "body": {
                      "type": "string",
                    },
                    "cwd": {
                      "type": "string",
                    },
                    "error": {
                      "type": "string",
                    },
                    "files": {
                      "items": {
                        "type": "string",
                      },
                      "type": "array",
                    },
                    "operation": {
                      "enum": [
                        "add",
                        "commit",
                      ],
                      "type": "string",
                    },
                    "subject": {
                      "type": "string",
                    },
                    "vault": {
                      "pattern": "^main-vault$|^project-vault$|^sub-vault:\\.mnemonic-.+$|^attached:[a-z0-9][-a-z0-9]*\\/\\.mnemonic(-.+)?$",
                      "type": "string",
                    },
                  },
                  "required": [
                    "subject",
                    "files",
                    "vault",
                    "error",
                  ],
                  "type": "object",
                },
                "instructions": {
                  "additionalProperties": false,
                  "properties": {
                    "forbidInferenceFromHistory": {
                      "type": "boolean",
                    },
                    "forbidInferenceFromTitleOrSummary": {
                      "type": "boolean",
                    },
                    "forbidParallelSameVaultRetries": {
                      "type": "boolean",
                    },
                    "preferToolReconciliation": {
                      "type": "boolean",
                    },
                    "rerunSameToolCallSerially": {
                      "type": "boolean",
                    },
                    "sourceOfTruth": {
                      "enum": [
                        "attemptedCommit",
                        "tool-response",
                      ],
                      "type": "string",
                    },
                    "useExactBody": {
                      "type": "boolean",
                    },
                    "useExactFiles": {
                      "type": "boolean",
                    },
                    "useExactSubject": {
                      "type": "boolean",
                    },
                  },
                  "required": [
                    "sourceOfTruth",
                    "useExactSubject",
                    "useExactBody",
                    "useExactFiles",
                    "forbidInferenceFromHistory",
                    "forbidInferenceFromTitleOrSummary",
                    "forbidParallelSameVaultRetries",
                    "preferToolReconciliation",
                    "rerunSameToolCallSerially",
                  ],
                  "type": "object",
                },
                "mutationApplied": {
                  "type": "boolean",
                },
                "rationale": {
                  "type": "string",
                },
                "recovery": {
                  "additionalProperties": false,
                  "properties": {
                    "allowed": {
                      "type": "boolean",
                    },
                    "kind": {
                      "enum": [
                        "manual-exact-git-recovery",
                        "rerun-tool-call-serial",
                        "no-manual-recovery",
                      ],
                      "type": "string",
                    },
                    "reason": {
                      "type": "string",
                    },
                  },
                  "required": [
                    "kind",
                    "allowed",
                    "reason",
                  ],
                  "type": "object",
                },
                "retrySafe": {
                  "type": "boolean",
                },
              },
              "required": [
                "recovery",
                "attemptedCommit",
                "mutationApplied",
                "retrySafe",
                "rationale",
                "instructions",
              ],
              "type": "object",
            },
          },
          "required": [
            "notePath",
            "embeddingPath",
            "embedding",
            "git",
            "durability",
          ],
          "type": "object",
        },
        "projectAssociation": {
          "type": "string",
        },
        "title": {
          "type": "string",
        },
        "toVault": {
          "pattern": "^main-vault$|^project-vault$|^sub-vault:\\.mnemonic-.+$|^attached:[a-z0-9][-a-z0-9]*\\/\\.mnemonic(-.+)?$",
          "type": "string",
        },
      },
      "required": [
        "action",
        "id",
        "fromVault",
        "toVault",
        "projectAssociation",
        "title",
        "persistence",
      ],
      "type": "object",
    },
    "title": "Move Memory",
  },
  {
    "annotations": {
      "destructiveHint": false,
      "idempotentHint": true,
      "openWorldHint": false,
      "readOnlyHint": true,
    },
    "description": "Use this when:
- You want fast orientation before starting work
- You need a synthesized overview instead of raw note listings

Do not use this when:
- You need exact note contents; use \`get\`
- You need direct semantic matches for a query; use \`recall\`

Returns: synthesized project summary, themes, anchors, orientation entry points with 1-hop previews, maintenance warnings, optional working-state recovery hints.

Typical next step:
- Use \`recall\` or \`list\` to drill down into specific areas.",
    "inputSchema": {
      "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
      "properties": {
        "anchorLimit": {
          "default": 5,
          "maximum": 10,
          "minimum": 1,
          "type": "integer",
        },
        "cwd": {
          "description": "Absolute path of the project working directory. Required for project-scoped routing, vault selection, and search boosting.",
          "type": "string",
        },
        "includeRelatedGlobal": {
          "default": false,
          "type": "boolean",
        },
        "maxPerTheme": {
          "default": 3,
          "maximum": 5,
          "minimum": 1,
          "type": "integer",
        },
        "recentLimit": {
          "default": 5,
          "maximum": 10,
          "minimum": 1,
          "type": "integer",
        },
        "relatedGlobalLimit": {
          "default": 3,
          "maximum": 5,
          "minimum": 1,
          "type": "integer",
        },
      },
      "required": [
        "cwd",
      ],
      "type": "object",
    },
    "name": "project_memory_summary",
    "outputSchema": {
      "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "properties": {
        "action": {
          "const": "project_summary_shown",
          "type": "string",
        },
        "anchors": {
          "items": {
            "additionalProperties": false,
            "properties": {
              "centrality": {
                "type": "number",
              },
              "connectionDiversity": {
                "type": "number",
              },
              "id": {
                "type": "string",
              },
              "title": {
                "type": "string",
              },
              "updatedAt": {
                "type": "string",
              },
            },
            "required": [
              "id",
              "title",
              "centrality",
              "connectionDiversity",
              "updatedAt",
            ],
            "type": "object",
          },
          "type": "array",
        },
        "maintenanceWarnings": {
          "description": "Advisory project memory health warnings derived from loaded metadata only.",
          "items": {
            "additionalProperties": false,
            "properties": {
              "code": {
                "description": "Stable warning code for a project memory maintenance condition.",
                "enum": [
                  "stale-temporary-notes",
                  "superseded-prune-candidates",
                  "weak-orientation-anchors",
                ],
                "type": "string",
              },
              "count": {
                "description": "Number of notes or conditions represented by this warning when applicable.",
                "type": "number",
              },
              "message": {
                "description": "Compact human-readable maintenance warning matching the text output.",
                "type": "string",
              },
              "sampleNotes": {
                "description": "Bounded sample of notes that triggered this warning.",
                "items": {
                  "additionalProperties": false,
                  "properties": {
                    "id": {
                      "description": "Memory id for a bounded sample note that triggered this warning.",
                      "type": "string",
                    },
                    "title": {
                      "description": "Title for a bounded sample note that triggered this warning.",
                      "type": "string",
                    },
                  },
                  "required": [
                    "id",
                    "title",
                  ],
                  "type": "object",
                },
                "type": "array",
              },
              "severity": {
                "description": "Advisory severity for the maintenance condition; warnings still require explicit user action.",
                "enum": [
                  "info",
                  "warning",
                ],
                "type": "string",
              },
              "suggestedAction": {
                "description": "Explicit next action the agent can take; never an automatic cleanup action.",
                "type": "string",
              },
            },
            "required": [
              "code",
              "severity",
              "message",
              "suggestedAction",
            ],
            "type": "object",
          },
          "type": "array",
        },
        "notes": {
          "additionalProperties": false,
          "properties": {
            "attachedVault": {
              "type": "number",
            },
            "mainVault": {
              "type": "number",
            },
            "privateProject": {
              "type": "number",
            },
            "projectVault": {
              "type": "number",
            },
            "total": {
              "type": "number",
            },
          },
          "required": [
            "total",
            "projectVault",
            "mainVault",
            "privateProject",
          ],
          "type": "object",
        },
        "orientation": {
          "additionalProperties": false,
          "properties": {
            "primaryEntry": {
              "additionalProperties": false,
              "properties": {
                "confidence": {
                  "enum": [
                    "high",
                    "medium",
                    "low",
                  ],
                  "type": "string",
                },
                "id": {
                  "type": "string",
                },
                "provenance": {
                  "additionalProperties": false,
                  "properties": {
                    "lastCommitHash": {
                      "type": "string",
                    },
                    "lastCommitMessage": {
                      "type": "string",
                    },
                    "lastUpdatedAt": {
                      "type": "string",
                    },
                    "recentlyChanged": {
                      "type": "boolean",
                    },
